1195
00:52:17,166 --> 00:52:19,733
       IN THE COUNTRY'S         
       MILITARY HISTORY.        

1196
00:52:19,802 --> 00:52:22,969
          "WEDNESDAY,           
      SEPTEMBER 27, 1944.       

1197
00:52:23,038 --> 00:52:27,574
  "BAHN STOPPED IN TO TELL ME   
THAT WE LOST 22 OUT OF 35 SHIPS.

1198
00:52:27,643 --> 00:52:31,711
   "WITHEY, GOLDEN, BOECHER,    
    ROBINSON, AND REYNOLDS      

1199
00:52:31,780 --> 00:52:33,246
       DIDN'T GET BACK."        

1200
00:52:33,315 --> 00:52:35,682
     JACK PELTON REMEMBERS      
        THAT DAY WELL.          

1201
00:52:35,751 --> 00:52:37,217
THEY CALLED ME                  
FOR THAT MISSION                

1202
00:52:37,286 --> 00:52:39,019
AND I HAD A PASS                
TO GO TO LONDON.                

1203
00:52:39,087 --> 00:52:41,555
AND I SHOWED THE SERGEANT       
MY PASS, AND HE SAID, "OKAY,"   

1204
00:52:41,623 --> 00:52:43,056
TOOK THE GUY                    
IN THE NEXT BUNK,               

1205
00:52:43,125 --> 00:52:44,791
AND HE NEVER CAME HOME.         

1206
00:52:44,860 --> 00:52:48,195
      THIRTY-NINE PLANES        
   FROM THE 445th BOMB GROUP    

1207
00:52:48,263 --> 00:52:51,831
SET OUT TO ATTACK A TANK FACTORY
      IN KASSEL, GERMANY.       

1208
00:52:51,900 --> 00:52:54,434
      BUT THE LEAD PLANE        
      MAKES A WRONG TURN,       

1209
00:52:54,503 --> 00:52:57,304
         AND THE 445th          
        GETS SEPARATED          

1210
00:52:57,372 --> 00:52:59,306
         FROM THE REST          
      OF THE COMBAT WING.       

1211
00:52:59,374 --> 00:53:03,310
  ALONE OVER ENEMY TERRITORY,   
  THE LIBERATORS ARE AMBUSHED   

1212
00:53:03,378 --> 00:53:07,948
 BY OVER 100 GERMAN FIGHTERS.   

1213
00:53:08,016 --> 00:53:13,019
  IN LESS THAN FOUR MINUTES,    
 116 AMERICAN PILOTS ARE DEAD.  

1214
00:53:13,088 --> 00:53:16,656
  SURVIVORS RETURNING TO BASE   
      RECOUNT THE HORROR.       

1215
00:53:16,725 --> 00:53:19,392
      THE AIR WAS FILLED        
    WITH BOMBERS BLOWING UP     

1216
00:53:19,461 --> 00:53:20,894
   AND FALLING BOMBER PARTS,    

1217
00:53:20,963 --> 00:53:23,129
    PARACHUTES, AND BODIES,     
        AND BODY PARTS.         

1218
00:53:23,198 --> 00:53:25,665
   IT WAS A REAL HOLOCAUST.     

1219
00:53:25,734 --> 00:53:27,734
  SOME OF THE GUYS CAME BACK,   
 THEY WERE ALMOST HYSTERICAL.   

1220
00:53:27,803 --> 00:53:29,302
       THEY COULD HARDLY        
      CONTAIN THEMSELVES.       

1221
00:53:29,371 --> 00:53:32,038
  THOUGH THE LOSS IS TRAGIC,    
       THE WAR GOES ON.         

1222
00:53:32,107 --> 00:53:34,841
  THE NEXT DAY, THE MILITARY    
  SENDS ANOTHER BOMBER GROUP    

1223
